title: My Kayle skin?
body: I haven't received my skin yet for the 10th anniversary. I got both the summoner icon and Kayle after opening a chest but did not receive the Riot Kayle. Help....

replies.body: The gifts are being sent out separately, so some players may not see everything all at once.  They are still being distributed per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), so it's not done just yet.  The goods will come!
